1. DEFINITIONS

   "Software" means the source code, binaries, plugins, configuration files,
   reports, telemetry payloads, and accompanying documentation contained in
   this repository (HealthCheckPS1) and any future versions tagged 2.0 or
   later.

   "AuthorityGate PSO Customer" means an organization with an active
   Professional Services Organization engagement contract in effect with
   AuthorityGate, Inc.

   "Production Use" means any execution of the Software where its outputs
   inform decisions for, or are delivered to, an organization other than the
   user's own personal lab or training environment - including but not
   limited to: customer engagements, internal corporate IT operations,
   managed-service-provider deliverables, and audit / compliance reports.

   "License Token" means a signed Ed25519 JWT issued by
   https://license.authoritygate.com that authorizes a named individual on
   a single machine to run the Software for a limited time window.


