   discretion.


6. TELEMETRY

   The Software submits run metadata to https://license.authoritygate.com on
   each authorized execution. This telemetry includes:

       - the licensee's email address
       - the machine fingerprint (SHA-256 of MachineGuid)
       - the Windows hostname of the runner
       - the timestamp the run started and ended
       - the FQDNs of the systems scanned (vCenter, Horizon, App Volumes,
         Unified Access Gateway, NSX, Active Directory)
       - the document author and customer engagement name as entered by
         the operator
       - aggregate plugin counts and severity-band counts of findings

   The Software does NOT transmit:
       - probe data (registry contents, software inventories, service lists,
         config dumps)
       - finding text (KB IDs, recommendations, fixes, evidence)
       - IP addresses of customer assets
       - credentials of any kind

   Use of the Software constitutes consent to this telemetry.


